{"tid":1079646,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"爸爸哺乳媽媽樂！日企推出「男人餵奶」神器","createTime":"2019-03-27T05:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-27T08:02:37.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f38b5c7b0c35c645ae462ef40da8d17be15ad15b","tid":1079646,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HZvJc1K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHZvJc1K.png&h=e1ebd470&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e63uS1Z.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe63uS1Z.png&h=c48c73e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男人常自誇除了生孩子、哺乳外，還有什麼不會？現在除了不能生孩子，哺乳也能幫上忙了！一家日本公司推出一款「男人哺乳」神器，讓男人體驗餵母奶的感覺，相信能有效促進父子間的親子關係，並減輕媽媽的育兒壓力。<br />\n<br />\n日本企業「電通」發明這款外型模仿女性乳房的哺乳背心，乳頭則是奶嘴，讓爸爸也可分體驗餵母奶的感覺，減輕媽媽負之餘，還可促進親子關係。<br />\n<br />\n《今日美國報》報導，哺乳背心暫訂名為「爸爸育兒助手」（FATHER&rsquo;S NURSING ASSISTANT），日前在美國德州奥斯汀一個展覽會中亮相，造型是模仿媽媽的胸部製作，觸感柔軟，其中一邊可以裝母奶，另一邊則有模仿乳頭的奶嘴，背心更可發熱，變成接近人的體溫，可以讓寶寶更安心舒適地吸奶。<br />\n<br />\n爸爸戴上哺乳背心後，可以雙手環抱孩子在胸口，然後像媽媽般哺乳。哺乳背心更裝有感應器，可記錄寶寶的進食及睡覺時間，資料會傳送至手機APP中，幫助父母了解及掌握寶寶的作息及吃奶習慣。<br />\n<br />\n電通表示，有研究指出父母間對餵哺小孩及哄睡都感到很大困難及壓力，而很多爸爸在育兒的方面參與程度往往較媽媽低，此款哺乳背心可提高爸爸對育兒參與度，從中減輕媽媽的負擔，讓父母及小孩都能有足夠的睡眠時間。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2740191\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2740191&d=vajnz719fThxN7XVIZyF5bBzIjlmttHRdZ2xAWa028c%3D&h=7df6446e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F2740191&h=bc4eefaa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/2740191</a>"},{"pid":"08061428f467a8a7de7fe0402373735ffe144b09","tid":1079646,"uid":106864,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:39:42.000Z","msg":"屌你仲以為爸爸哺媽媽嘅乳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n負皮係俾標題嘅"},{"pid":"b699e565c7473a1306078b9e9c4b150e74a35f34","tid":1079646,"uid":32380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:40:36.000Z","msg":"爸爸哺乳媽媽樂？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfa2f51f1d5aec836ce04f53d12888266d0d5bf","tid":1079646,"uid":75232,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:42:14.000Z","msg":"正丫喂，有咗佢老婆夜晚就唔使咁辛苦起身餵奶<br />\n<br />\n利申：仲有個半月做老豆"},{"pid":"af53b31c17889a2e073a095ce5f81f13a8da7b0e","tid":1079646,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:43:49.000Z","msg":"如果個呀媽本身貧乳呢 會唔會食唔慣"},{"pid":"b4654d1df9ee9e13d34f8ad6aa1a02d2ff2d849c","tid":1079646,"uid":470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:44:35.000Z","msg":"電通做埋科技研發？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6a8dc04029eb464b4de22c8f70bd0836171996e","tid":1079646,"uid":2974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:46:23.000Z","msg":"要入手了，配埋飛機杯用"},{"pid":"4616cd673a6acad7a3b39c85f5618cb6473245fe","tid":1079646,"uid":13592,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T05:47:23.000Z","msg":"細路錢真好賺 我完全覺得多鳩餘<br />\n<br />\n利申 有兩個小朋友"},{"pid":"c420f446c9bf3c0b411fbb695d4d543fbf4da277","tid":1079646,"uid":28195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T07:59:07.000Z","msg":"個奶假既"},{"pid":"726ba336a57d22195a8b6e2c101937566b127b46","tid":1079646,"uid":136985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:01:09.000Z","msg":"如果跟返港女身型仲work唔work<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac2f52b2ad126e40958f0d560e95f65b330e209","tid":1079646,"uid":35014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T08:01:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb3a78099d154d7e2c15af94a168d4e86b99f4dc","tid":1079646,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"